---
title: Pesto Chicken and Mozzarella Salad with spinach and balsamic glaze
description: This spinach-based salad contains many exciting elements. Oregano-coated chicken provides protein while also creating a herbaceous taste that compliments the pesto dressing beautifully. Roasted pepper, juicy tomatoes and fresh mozzarella also make an appearance.
